{"tid":1425513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依家仲係深水埗嘅手足入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-06T18:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:50:28.000Z","uid":289442,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"54ba558aa355b18234c24eba77d4835379bca1e7","tid":1425513,"uid":289442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:29:54.000Z","msg":"我知你係現場睇唔到其他嘢<br />\n但係睇番今次班狗明顯想R民意<br />\n拜託你哋咁夜唔好咁大聲撚狗啦<br />\n街坊又散晒啦 埋個尾做番靚啲好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n啲狗係咁做啲親民嘢比主流影<br />\n我都好撚嬲，但係記得撚狗目的係要佢出醜<br />\n先唔好自己出醜先 頭先隔住個mon聽到哨子聲都好撚嘈<br />\n現場居民真係唔知點諗<br />\n<br />\n預撚咗比人屌<br />\n今次白衫想R民意 但係行動果班柒晒係好彩<br />\n唔能夠擔保下次都係咁好彩 希望在場手足撚還撚<br />\n去到咁上下就停 要令街坊覺得擾民嘅係狗 唔係我哋"},{"pid":"62a4c09d7919c8b066caea195ff907481bc84b11","tid":1425513,"uid":289442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:32:19.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a4cb81e9dd7b30add0cdd33d3f46122ab4a853e6","tid":1425513,"uid":289442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:32:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"64e0a5a0a5bcfd72a57a9876abead1c4015cb3cb","tid":1425513,"uid":289442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:32:40.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f659301b3b1aba8247281c63c8670487383e4087","tid":1425513,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:34:01.000Z","msg":"agree 適量就得"},{"pid":"8564bc4a0ab33aa1790e23c65e0cb6384a815c2d","tid":1425513,"uid":234402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:39:09.000Z","msg":"呢個絕對唔係分化<br />\n係策略"},{"pid":"c69767a24a4db216c30173eb25810aa97fd6910b","tid":1425513,"uid":289442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:50:28.000Z","msg":"暫時未比人屌 希望唔好有人屌分化"}]}